<subSubSection id="6ABAFBF0DE67312B7448FADF5CCA943A" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="59" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="FEFB08C863F8FDB1336A94E67FE2F334" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A3E890A40165B58D78637BC5C8B61D42" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
<taxonomicName id="F7CCEE31F116E26460A11B25B4688584" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus hordeaceus" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hordeaceus">
<emphasis id="47720207994E3BD5B75D3623B86EED48" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">Bromus hordeaceus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. is a very variable species with a complex nomenclatural history at subspecies level. The origin of many problems in the group is the name 
<taxonomicName id="9A2818B6313F042C7C9A0A73C6F06D4C" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="45575EA2D35BBE1BDC368AD82A58B00B" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd, Fl. Loire-Inf. (
<bibRefCitation id="127683A4B5845C8FD639FC9FE6033CA3" author="Lloyd, J" journalOrPublisher="Repertorium Specierum Novarum Regni Vegetabilis" pageId="10" pageNumber="63" refId="B21" refString="Lloyd, J, 1844. Flore de la Loire-Inferieure. Prosper Sevire, Nantes. https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k984852/f4.image" title="Flore de la Loire-Inferieure. Prosper Sevire, Nantes. https: // gallica. bnf. fr / ark: / 12148 / bpt 6 k 984852 / f 4. image" year="1844">Lloyd 1844</bibRefCitation>
: 314-315), which was invalidly published as a provisional name &quot;je proposerais, si 
<normalizedToken id="2B6073AEEED9813A33CFBD89CADE0FD6" originalValue="c’était">c'etait</normalizedToken>
une 
<normalizedToken id="93734270D6087DE99431A5F3743F555A" originalValue="espèce">espece</normalizedToken>
nouvelle, de 
<normalizedToken id="015427ADB946434EA4473C55CE8AA1E4" originalValue="l’appeler">l'appeler</normalizedToken>
<taxonomicName id="42A921ED6E92B23729215DE81A07CEB4" genus="Br." lsidName="Br. molliformis" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="9D7CEF8E27BE48ABBF58BB755BE3CDB6" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">Br. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
&quot;. The name was later validated as 
<taxonomicName id="E3C840DC0AED7F7F7715355F1FD7AA84" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="C6301A2FF6103CEB50D39439E44E6C73" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">Bromus molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd ex Billot, Fl. Gall. &amp; Germ. Exsicc. (Haguenau) 2: Cent. 14. 1854. Billot supplies a brief description for &quot;cette 
<normalizedToken id="2B3C63A7E4D38AB73FCA2E7368EF49EE" originalValue="espèce">espece</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="112FBFD305C5CE3DCED2CD512148C98F" originalValue="donnée">donnee</normalizedToken>
par M.Lloyd dans sa 
<emphasis id="F565FD9B3BEC017C1320FEE822F4FE62" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
Flore de la 
<normalizedToken id="29F31E212AE9EF0036DB24BDAEEBD63E" originalValue="Loire-Inférieure">Loire-Inferieure</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
sous le nom de 
<taxonomicName id="098BC64B050EA747B75EFCA80B76E7A9" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. divaricatitus" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="divaricatitus">
<emphasis id="31B3D811A5D63B9A38086E78CB9260CD" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. divaricatitus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Rohde?&quot; Billot (Feb. 1854: 297-298) neglects to mention several details of 
<normalizedToken id="DC03431296EFAC028CAD81F2EA325D2B" originalValue="Lloyd’s">Lloyd's</normalizedToken>
description of 
<taxonomicName id="347A5FCA3E6ABC9ADB0A9C971F32438E" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="9791024378168BBB282018C8A3EFFAA3" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and describes the species as follows:
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F732289726B4AA87832E719CE686ED69" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
&quot;Racine fibreuse. Chaume de 2-4 
<normalizedToken id="CD214E8D5490B244A6E0030307B227F3" originalValue="décimètres">decimetres</normalizedToken>
. Feuilles et graines 
<normalizedToken id="1AE85ED030B1D174BA0F90D8681BB101" originalValue="inférieures">inferieures</normalizedToken>
mollement poilues. Panicule oblongue, droite, 
<normalizedToken id="BD90F52CA236DF95F6656ABC629734EC" originalValue="étalée">etalee</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="1A904ADBD4AE2473F8A05ED2AB143FF3" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
<normalizedToken id="180960F9DBCFEA143A1F132BDBD2066C" originalValue="resserrée">resserree</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="A8A39D7E25D5C1339EA0560B62C56404" originalValue="après">apres</normalizedToken>
la floraison
</emphasis>
; 
<normalizedToken id="53991A5521A0A4E9D81710097946E0E8" originalValue="pédoncules">pedoncules</normalizedToken>
courts, simples. Epillets oblongs, 
<normalizedToken id="9A14ADF8BD941A1C0E29C09561DB1ED2" originalValue="étalés">etales</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="C62FD10E61539AF7E5EFC5B2C72A95AF" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">velus</emphasis>
; 
<normalizedToken id="E6BF837292FEC93F76A6D7854BD7D9AF" originalValue="arête">arete</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="58D41432A6A7875C3B35EF5CF6B0863D" originalValue="égalant">egalant</normalizedToken>
la glumelle, 
<normalizedToken id="B6B57F04C539EA7D7312653125A5047D" originalValue="d’abord">d'abord</normalizedToken>
droite, 
<normalizedToken id="7103CD2CF45C0A7439C7FF427CA0271D" originalValue="à">a</normalizedToken>
la fin 
<emphasis id="33A9CC5A59EAE169508938C780692E9C" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
<normalizedToken id="DF3BF6A6B1A24F112BEB931F9F6010B1" originalValue="tortillée">tortillee</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="1EDAB68DF82D6CB5D2E6DC89ABE4A7DF" originalValue="divariquée">divariquee</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, 
<normalizedToken id="3E03809F4622F04CC8BAF5E4691CA36B" originalValue="insérée">inseree</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="9AA428EB1AD7FBA79CCC2359C2DFEF24" originalValue="à">a</normalizedToken>
1 1/2 
<normalizedToken id="9F2A0EA0A6CB1342C2B6E1986C216AB6" originalValue="millimètre">millimetre</normalizedToken>
du sommet obtus, 
<normalizedToken id="45ADDB03A6641E661418693CC0724365" originalValue="échancré”">echancre&quot;</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CC596593556AC0C205491F86D7E6096E" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
<bibRefCitation id="7960AAB86B74B319FDB548A878A3573A" author="Billot, C" journalOrPublisher="Archives de la Flore de France et d'Allemagne" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" pagination="287 - 298" refId="B5" refString="Billot, C, 1854. Flora Galliae et Germaniae Exsiccata. Archives de la Flore de France et d'Allemagne 1: 287 - 298" title="Flora Galliae et Germaniae Exsiccata." volume="1" year="1854">Billot (1854)</bibRefCitation>
publishes the first validating description for 
<taxonomicName id="43B652833434729469F314DF009C7242" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="F4197900F0D3E4445BCC1F2A2C144964" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">Bromus molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. He includes the reference of the features to differentiate the new species from the closely related 
<taxonomicName id="F89BEB6A3641CBEEA40CCE6D65675E39" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. hordeaceus" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="hordeaceus">
<emphasis id="5068CD39DFF08C4448952B023EA28D7C" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. hordeaceus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. and from 
<taxonomicName id="B11AFA1FB4E08E5C1D954B59B86DDE15" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. divaricatus" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="divaricatus">
<emphasis id="F59188C020173CC4449A82FC539CF3EF" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. divaricatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Rhode. He sold his exsiccata to several herbaria. There is not a register of those herbaria. Currently, some of them are included in P where some original specimens with its species number (1386) are preserved. Additionally, there are several names and combinations at several ranks, both validly and invalidly published and various nomenclatural changes. Nevertheless, 
<taxonomicName id="1B0D6DE7D08413FFF54972EF7C2DEC11" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="D9BBC1104666985070B6C9B4CF7FD6C2" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd ex Billot remained untypified and still lacked a stable nomenclature.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="55C79B7254FBFCC9992B75E3392CD2F1" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="59" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">
<taxonomicName id="CC9AADFAF14F40D343636484960FA9D4" authority="W.D.J.Koch, 1844 (Parl.)" authorityName="W.D.J.Koch, 1844 (Parl.)" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Serrafalcus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Serrafalcus lloydianus" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lloydianus">
<emphasis id="F0509A629E8AFD61087CD559BB373FD2" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">Serrafalcus lloydianus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Godr. &amp; Gren. (1855: 591) is a superfluous name for 
<taxonomicName id="E1A3F7FC613FBF209F2450A6CC0B610A" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="03F0835BAE9EF53F0644453ABE6CF56A" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd ex Billot. 
<bibRefCitation id="618B195D6181228F3B4B68AEE0A6D103" author="Grenier, M" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" refId="B10" refString="Grenier, M, Godron, M, 1855. Flore de France. J.-B Bailliere, Paris. https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/6122574" title="Flore de France. J. - B Bailliere, Paris. https: // biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 6122574" year="1855">Grenier and Godron (1855)</bibRefCitation>
listed several synonyms, including &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="18B6A5A89BEE1F4C10CB1CE22F29EDFB" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. divaricatus" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="divaricatus">
<emphasis id="E55FA2DC45BC6135536AD61EA8B7B9B6" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. divaricatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Lloyd non Rhode&quot; and 
<taxonomicName id="356B15FBBC69EB78F0E9F86CAA551830" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="5" pageNumber="58" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="435426DBB9F19D535715233752E1CBE1" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="58">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd ex Billot 
<pageBreakToken id="955321B8C9FB1A5F1B66044C4D845F4C" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" start="start">[</pageBreakToken>
sub. 
<taxonomicName id="9FDC1961856767B093D2B9BD27A5FF02" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="63BCA4E315BE0972A5D1EE0DD46F6829" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Lloyd]. They also mention 
<normalizedToken id="B2C11E26CC1431E8C69A9ED2631CFD71" originalValue="Billot’s">Billot's</normalizedToken>
exsiccate n. 1586; and include his new species in the complex of species having 
<normalizedToken id="B05C02D6DA62AB091B8DBF75024C98C5" originalValue="“arête">&quot;arete</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="0375EEFCE3C4F095B7924132E60F1BA6" originalValue="…">...</normalizedToken>
tordue sur 
<normalizedToken id="E222B842C625818F15B32D6E01AEC0BE" originalValue="elle-même">elle-meme</normalizedToken>
et 
<normalizedToken id="52F5FEFFC7E017BD2C383738BAE6493B" originalValue="divariquée”">divariquee&quot;</normalizedToken>
. Therefore, this name does not need a Lectoype as it is a superfluous and illegitimate renaming (Art. 52.1) of 
<taxonomicName id="FE420F49609098237DEC3E9898288463" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="A0A2C23A1ED7C374720F3ACC00091247" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">Bromus molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd ex Billot and has the same type we select here for that name.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4725BA5625E0A0EC94D4488E5CF6DD80" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
<bibRefCitation id="A8D84A5F93FD771F9F53017C706AC4B4" author="Bonnier, G" journalOrPublisher="Archives de la Flore de France et d'Allemagne" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" refId="B6" refString="Bonnier, G, Layens, G, 1894. Tableaux synoptiques des plantes vasculaires de la Flore de la France. Paul Dupont, Paris. https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.323" title="Tableaux synoptiques des plantes vasculaires de la Flore de la France. Paul Dupont, Paris. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 323" year="1894">Bonnier and Layens (1894</bibRefCitation>
: 369) describe 
<taxonomicName id="A5ADD86D0745373D765ABA043B7CE8BC" authority="Guss. subsp. divaricatus" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="subsp." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus intermedius" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intermedius" subspecies="divaricatus">Bromus intermedius Guss. subsp. divaricatus</taxonomicName>
Bonnier &amp; Layens, based on 
<taxonomicName id="3E5F7369D4BD62AE00B06906FB95BFA6" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. divaricatus" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" rank="species" species="divaricatus">
<emphasis id="C350474A0CAF2CBECF8104C89699C9FE" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">B. divaricatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[sensu] Lloyd, non Rhode, with the characteristics of 
<normalizedToken id="A849F253CC96DEEBCAA0C7C9498451AD" originalValue="Lloyd’s">Lloyd's</normalizedToken>
plant. 
<bibRefCitation id="B8EDDAEF88ED5230CE824455EC459ABE" author="Kerguelen, M" journalOrPublisher="Lejeunia" pageId="10" pageNumber="63" refId="B18" refString="Kerguelen, M, 1981. N 8913 [17] Bromusmolliformis. Societe pour l'Echange des Plantes Vasculaires de l'Europe et du Bassin Mediterraneen 18: 27." title="N 8913 [17] Bromusmolliformis. Societe pour l'Echange des Plantes Vasculaires de l'Europe et du Bassin Mediterraneen 18: 27." year="1981">
<normalizedToken id="B317815AB5D147949B9278B17742CAB9" originalValue="Kerguélen">Kerguelen</normalizedToken>
(1981
</bibRefCitation>
: 27) combines it to 
<taxonomicName id="A22C2E9B1004EB95E56341320A8E60B1" authority="subsp divaricatus" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="subsp" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus hordeaceus" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hordeaceus" subspecies="divaricatus">Bromus hordeaceus subsp divaricatus</taxonomicName>
(Bonnier &amp; Layens) 
<normalizedToken id="96528A89686615EFD3DEACA858F356C0" originalValue="Kerguélen">Kerguelen</normalizedToken>
. Bonnier and Layens type material is unknown (
<bibRefCitation id="AA54E84AF9FAF45353F7703CAD2F4B84" author="Stafleu, FA" journalOrPublisher="Feddes Repertorium" pageId="10" pageNumber="63" refId="B28" refString="Stafleu, FA, Cowan, RS, 1976. Taxonomic literature (2nd ed.) Utrecht: Bohn, Scheltema &amp; Holkema, v.1: A-G. http://www.sil.si.edu/DigitalCollections/tl-2/browse.cfm?vol=1page/11" title="Taxonomic literature (2 nd ed.) Utrecht: Bohn, Scheltema &amp; Holkema, v. 1: A-G. http: // www. sil. si. edu / DigitalCollections / tl- 2 / browse. cfm? vol = 1  page / 11" year="1976">Stafleu and Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="8A3403F8C35AE418F82E265DC999BF35" author="Kerguelen, M" journalOrPublisher="Lejeunia" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 343" refId="B17" refString="Kerguelen, M, 1975. Les Gramineae (Poaceae) de la Flore Francaise. Essai de mise au point taxonomique et nomenclaturale. Lejeunia 75: 1 - 343" title="Les Gramineae (Poaceae) de la Flore Francaise. Essai de mise au point taxonomique et nomenclaturale." volume="75" year="1975">
<normalizedToken id="63C2DA302F988E5FD77C37FBD9E38D5B" originalValue="Kerguélen">Kerguelen</normalizedToken>
(1975
</bibRefCitation>
: 104) mentions 
<normalizedToken id="EB69091A7705E04B5D8B49A4328B65C7" originalValue="Lloyd’s">Lloyd's</normalizedToken>
type material is in herbarium NTM, pointing out two localities &quot;Pornic, Saint Brevin&quot; indicated by Lloyd. Nevertheless, no original material is preserved in NTM (Mary Laury Guerin, Com. pers. 2018).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FB7B00B67940D393F9D0AEB6BDA13C6E" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
<taxonomicName id="FACE0F7ADE7B65D03CE998DFC30905B2" authority="L." class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="var." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus hordeaceus var. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="hordeaceus" variety="molliformis">Bromus hordeaceus L. var. molliformis</taxonomicName>
(J.Lloyd ex Billot) 
<bibRefCitation id="AB47C6DEF694807D6348ACFA1CDAFCF7" author="Halacsy, E" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" refId="B13" refString="Halacsy, E, 1904. Conspectus Florae Graecae III. Guilelmi Engelmann, Lipsiae. http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=2294&amp;Pagina=1" title="Conspectus Florae Graecae III. Guilelmi Engelmann, Lipsiae. http: // bibdigital. rjb. csic. es / spa / Libro. php? Libro = 2294 &amp; Pagina = 1" year="1904">
<normalizedToken id="B267303969EF088A61DD1F5140875C3F" originalValue="Halácsy">Halacsy</normalizedToken>
(1904
</bibRefCitation>
: 396). This is another combination of 
<taxonomicName id="4D9C5375132BBC82F44BFD390853D68B" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="33FC3FBBCD797C64863C352091B7DBF9" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd and 
<normalizedToken id="FA87DA5787900B9A41A34B8818743EF8" originalValue="Halácsy">Halacsy</normalizedToken>
pointed out its main traits &quot;Panicula magis conferta, ramis brevissime, spiculis densius et longius velutinu-pilosis, aristis demum extrorso subcurvatis&quot;.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BA5845C8C2C4628E19BC354C45B49485" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
<taxonomicName id="4D2DDCA7BABB749D27D7747FBF6872FA" authority="L. subsp. molliformis" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="subsp." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus hordeaceus" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hordeaceus" subspecies="molliformis">Bromus hordeaceus L. subsp. molliformis</taxonomicName>
(J.Lloyd) Maire &amp; Weiller (1955: 255). This post-1953 combination, without direct citation to the basionym, nor to a potentially validating Latin description, but only to &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="A9BE69F2053E3510CB58D76803C3DB67" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="26CFC6B3916209E659E496A032D2DE67" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">Bromus molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Lloyd, Fl. Loire-Inf. 315 (1844)&quot;, is another combination not validly published.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="73327DD3242CD04DA5FCF743541DBC42" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
As 
<taxonomicName id="C3F2A328896E9DB00242F2AAC36A0F45" authority="subsp. divaricatus" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="subsp." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus intermedius" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intermedius" subspecies="divaricatus">Bromus intermedius subsp. divaricatus</taxonomicName>
Bonnier &amp; Layens is an untypified name, we choose, as lectotype, the figure in 
<bibRefCitation id="D3DA9F3E1A99DE1271DE6CAE6646F27D" author="Bonnier, G" journalOrPublisher="Archives de la Flore de France et d'Allemagne" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" refId="B6" refString="Bonnier, G, Layens, G, 1894. Tableaux synoptiques des plantes vasculaires de la Flore de la France. Paul Dupont, Paris. https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.323" title="Tableaux synoptiques des plantes vasculaires de la Flore de la France. Paul Dupont, Paris. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 323" year="1894">Bonnier and Layens (1894</bibRefCitation>
: 369) that is definitely original material. However, as is common with figures, it is difficult to observe some diagnostic characteristics. Thus, we select, as epitype, a specimen collected by Lloyd, conserved in BM, consistent with the protologue. It is a sheet bearing two collections. We choose the specimen on the left from Pornichet (barcode BM001067302).
</paragraph>
<caption id="58C9A06E26AB2F37207B58FF6B7D684B" ID-Zenodo-Dep="2702123" doi="10.3897/phytokeys.119.30254.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/297552" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" start="Figure 5" startId="F5">
<paragraph id="0D9D3B033F1161D092FA6FB381195E0F" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
<emphasis id="4CFFE6C04217E2A61D00DE13957577F9" bold="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">Figure 5.</emphasis>
The epitype of 
<taxonomicName id="830D44897F44D48E973DBBFB96659BD4" authority="L. subsp divaricatus" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="subsp" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus hordeaceus" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hordeaceus" subspecies="divaricatus">Bromus hordeaceus L. subsp divaricatus</taxonomicName>
(Bonnier &amp; Layens) 
<normalizedToken id="4B8F35947433EA4315A166D223C73C43" originalValue="Kerguélen">Kerguelen</normalizedToken>
is the specimen on the left with barcode BM001067302 (collected and identified by Lloyd as 
<taxonomicName id="88CBED12052A5E162DF43A5844FE406D" family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="AFAD0CDFD794E211155F96657712DFA5" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">B. molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; preserved at BM (Permanent URL: http://data.nhm.ac.uk/object/9a6e0684-9e9b-4951-ac7e-ba13ad34ed31). Reproduced with permission.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="2395C39555EA01CDCFACE100675ABFE8" ID-Zenodo-Dep="2702125" doi="10.3897/phytokeys.119.30254.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/297553" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" start="Figure 6" startId="F6">
<paragraph id="1FE3D8B17320360B7010865A52483094" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">
<emphasis id="E54CF7DE034E671330906651A74A0B3C" bold="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">Figure 6.</emphasis>
Lectotype for 
<taxonomicName id="8F3C243B5018C4010F815EF8C262F15C" class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus molliformis" order="Poales" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="molliformis">
<emphasis id="7369E4DFB3CED0A4071A0E4704558033" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="59">Bromus molliformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
J.Lloyd ex Billot at P. It is a specimen preserved at the MNHN Collection Vascular plants. Specimen with barcode P02381530. (Available at http://coldb.mnhn.fr/catalognumber/mnhn/p/p02381530) Reproduced with permission.
</paragraph>
</caption>
